quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  33,44,"Hiwrondiral gom…óim…ďe …ďen √Īalnde …ďe hawroyte e Joomi ma…ď…ďe, ko "kisiyee e da…óugol kala bone", Alla maranii …ďe mbarjaari teddundi, ndin woni Aljanna Makko on, njo…ďdi ma…ď…ďe e ko …ďe …óoftii Mo kon, …ďe wo…ó…óitii e yeddugol Mo."
  33,45,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men nulirii ma e yim…ďe …ďen, fii yo a seedito e ma…ď…ďe, wonnde a yottinii ko nula-…óaa e ma…ď…ďe kon, e fii wewlinirgol gom…óim…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe, kon ko Alla marani …ďe ka Aljanna, e hul…ďingol heefer…ďe …ďen, kon ko Alla hebilani …ďe e lepte Makko."
  33,46,"Men nulirii ma fahin, noddiroowo e wootin…óingol Alla, …óoftoroo Mo yamirooje Makko …óen, Men nulir maa kadi ndaygu jal…ďungu, ngu kala faalaa…óo peewal ndayginorta."
  33,47,"Humpitu gom…óim…ďe Alla …ďen, golloo…ďe ko O sar'inani …ďe kon, huunde welaynde …ďe, wonnde hino woodani …ďe ka Alla senii…óo On, …ďural mawnungal: moftungal wallugol …ďe aduna, e malnugol …ďe laakara, naatugol Aljanna."
  33,48,"Wata a …óofto heefer…ďe …ďen e naafiqii…ďe …ďen, e kon ko …ďe nodditorta e falagol diina Alla kan, …óuurno …ďe. Hino hasii ka …óum wa…óata …ďe gom…óina ko addan-…óaa …ďe kon. Fawu e Alla fiyakuuji maa …óin, wano faabeede e ay…ďe maa. Sabu Alla yonii fawtotoo…óo, Mo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen fawotoo e mun aduna e laakara."
  33,49,"Ko onon yo …ďe gom…óim…ďe Alla, …ďe golli ko O sar'inani …ďe kon, si on humanii rew…ďe gom…óim…ďe …ďen dewgal, refti on seerii …ďe ado on yottaade e ma…ď…ďe, haray alanaa on e ma…ď…ďe, edda woo, foti ko limirtee…óo laa…ďal maa limirtee…óo lebbi, tawde rengaaji ma…ď…ďe …óin no laa…ďiri waaseede yottagol e ma…ď…ďe. Haray dakmitirii …ďe jawle mon …óen, yeru mon on, fii jeejugol …ďe ja…ďugol cergal ngal, jonnitiron …ďe maw…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, ko aldaa e lorrugol …ďe."
  33,50,"Ko an yo Annabiijo ! Men daginanii ma suddii…ďe maa …ďe jonnu-…óaa teŇče …ďen, e …ďen hor…ďe …ďe jeyu-…óaa, …ďe Alla ye…óu-maa e dahaa…ďe …ďen. Men daginanii ma kadi resugol jiw…ďe bappa maa …ďen, e jiw…ďe gorgilaa…ďe maa …ďen, e jiw…ďe kaawu maa …ďen, e jiw…ďe neeniraa…ďe maa; …ďen feridu…ďe e maa…óa Makka haa Madiina. Men daginanan maa kadi resugol suddii…óo gom…óin…óo, ye…óu…óo ma hoore-mun, ko aldaa e teŇče, si tawii hi…óa yi…ói resude mo. Resugol on ye…óu…óo hoore-mun non, ko heeranii …óum Annabiijo on (yo o his), dagantaako go…ó…óo goo e mofte …óen. Gom…óii Me…óen anndi ko Men wa…ó…óini e gom…óim…ďe …ďen kon, fii suddii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen; woni dagantaako …ďe resugol …ďuri rew…ďe nayo, Me…óen anndi kadi ko Men sar'inani …ďe kon e hor…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen; woni hino daganoo …ďe dakmitorgol …ďen, no …ďe haajiri, yeru ko …ďe yi…ói e ma…ď…ďe. Men daginanii ma ko jantaa koo, e ko Men daginanaali wo…ó…ďe goo, fii wata …ďi…óteende wonu e maa…óa. Alla siforii haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Hinnotoo…óo …ďe."